-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"width:50%;margin:auto;border:solid 3px #32CD32;background-color:#00FF00;text-align:center;clear:both\">\n<p><b>NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！</b><br />\n<a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN\" title=\"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\">了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"languages\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/Meatball\" title=\"Meatball\">English</a></b>\n<p><span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n&#160;&#8226;&#32;<span lang=\"zh-CN\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">中文（中国大陆）‎</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-brown\">%</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Meatball.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Meatball.png\" src=\"/images/0/0d/Meatball.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>肉丸\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>5 <a href=\"/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"金币\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>营养值\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E5%80%BC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"营养值 (page does not exist)\">5</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>食用所需回合数\n</th>\n<td>1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">1</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>行为\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"行为 (page does not exist)\">肉类</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>肉丸</b>（meatball）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%82%89%E7%B1%BB&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"肉类 (page does not exist)\">肉类</a><a href=\"/wiki/%E5%8F%AF%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"可食用品\">可食用品</a>。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">描述</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E8.8E.B7.E5.8F.96\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">获取</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#.E5.AE.A0.E7.89.A9\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">宠物</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#.E6.89.B9.E9.87.8F.E5.8F.98.E5.BD.A2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">批量变形</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#SlashTHEM\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">SlashTHEM</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">百科文本</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p>对下列石质物品施放<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%82%B9%E7%9F%B3%E6%88%90%E8%82%89%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%E4%B9%A6&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"点石成肉魔法书 (page does not exist)\">点石成肉</a><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%AF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"法术 (page does not exist)\">法术</a>会将其转化为肉丸（<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"玻璃 (page does not exist)\">玻璃</a>不会转化为肉丸）：\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B2%A9%E7%9F%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"岩石 (page does not exist)\">岩石</a></li>\n<li>贵重的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%AE%9D%E7%9F%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"宝石 (page does not exist)\">宝石</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E7%9F%B3%E5%A4%B4&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"灰色的石头 (page does not exist)\">灰色的石头</a></li>\n<li>体型为微小，或者非肉质的怪物的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%9B%95%E5%83%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"雕像 (page does not exist)\">雕像</a></li></ul>\n<p>除上述手段和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%AE%B8%E6%84%BF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"许愿 (page does not exist)\">许愿</a>之外，肉丸无法通过其他途径生成。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"描述\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\">描述</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"食用\">食用</a>肉丸会获得5点<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E5%80%BC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"营养值 (page does not exist)\">营养值</a>，并打破<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"素食主义 (page does not exist)\">素食主义</a>和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"绝对素食 (page does not exist)\">绝对素食</a>行为。肉丸可以用于<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A9%AF%E6%9C%8D&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"驯服 (page does not exist)\">驯服</a><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%82%89%E9%A3%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"肉食 (page does not exist)\">肉食</a>类<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%AE%B6%E7%95%9C&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"家畜 (page does not exist)\">家畜</a>，也可以用作肉食类<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"宠物 (page does not exist)\">宠物</a>的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%8B%9B%E5%BE%85%E7%89%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"招待物 (page does not exist)\">招待物</a>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<h3><span id=\"获取\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E8.8E.B7.E5.8F.96\">获取</span></h3>\n<p>由于点石成肉魔法书比较难获取，法术的施放难度也比较大，因此非<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"医生 (page does not exist)\">医生</a>职业的角色要获取肉丸是比较难的。<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B7%AB%E5%B8%88&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"巫师 (page does not exist)\">巫师</a>和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%88&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"牧师 (page does not exist)\">牧师</a>的起始物品中有随机魔法书，因此有可能开局就获得点石成肉。只要学会了点石成肉法术，玩家就可以轻松地获得大量肉丸：只需要收集大量的岩石（击碎<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B7%A8%E7%9F%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"巨石 (page does not exist)\">巨石</a>和雕像都可以掉落大量岩石），堆成一堆，然后对它们施法即可。\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"宠物\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.AE.A0.E7.89.A9\">宠物</span></h3>\n<p>肉丸的营养价值不高，因此常用于喂食肉食宠物以提高其驯服度，或是提升<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%8D%A1%E6%8B%BE%E5%BA%A6&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"捡拾度 (page does not exist)\">捡拾度</a>以<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%81%B7%E7%AA%83%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"偷窃商店 (page does not exist)\">偷窃商店</a>，你也可以在危急情况下用肉丸驯服敌对的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%8C%AB&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"猫 (page does not exist)\">猫</a>或<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%8B%97&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"狗 (page does not exist)\">狗</a>。\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"批量变形\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.89.B9.E9.87.8F.E5.8F.98.E5.BD.A2\">批量变形</span></h3>\n<p>由于可以大量获取，因此肉丸非常适合用作<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%98%E5%BD%A2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"批量变形 (page does not exist)\">批量变形</a>对象，以获取其他有实用价值的食物，如<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%85%B0%E5%B7%B4%E6%96%AF%E7%89%87\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"兰巴斯片\">兰巴斯片</a>、<a href=\"/wiki/%E8%8F%A0%E8%8F%9C\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"菠菜\">菠菜</a>罐头、<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%B8%A1%E8%9B%87%E8%9B%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"鸡蛇蛋 (page does not exist)\">鸡蛇蛋</a>等。不过，由于蛋和罐头的生成具有很高的随机性，因此要获得特定怪物的罐头或蛋可能需要变形非常多的肉丸。需要更多金钱的情况下，玩家也可以将批量变形肉丸得到的食物在<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"商店 (page does not exist)\">商店</a>里出售来获取金钱。\n</p><p>一次变形过多的肉丸可能会导致它们变成<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%82%89%E9%AD%94%E5%83%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"肉魔像 (page does not exist)\">肉魔像</a>。由于魔像的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%E6%8A%97%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%88%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%89&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"魔法抗性（怪物） (page does not exist)\">MR</a>很低，因此你可以故意利用这个机制，搭配驯服怪物的魔法来制造肉魔像宠物。你还可以通过用<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%B8%A1%E8%9B%87&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"鸡蛇 (page does not exist)\">鸡蛇</a>尸体攻击它来将它变成更强力的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%9F%B3%E9%AD%94%E5%83%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"石魔像 (page does not exist)\">石魔像</a>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>肉丸最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.3.0\" title=\"NetHack 3.3.0\">NetHack 3.3.0</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Meatball/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SlashTHEM\">SlashTHEM</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/SlashTHEM\" title=\"SlashTHEM\">SlashTHEM</a>, meatballs can be randomly generated, and can be sold in general <a href=\"/wiki/Store\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Store\">stores</a> and delicatessens.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"百科文本\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\">百科文本</span></h2><div class=\"nhencyclopedia\">\n<div class=\"poem\">\n<p>Some hae meat and canna eat,<br />\nAnd some would eat that want it;<br />\nBut we hae meat, and we can eat,<br />\nSae let the Lord be thankit.<br />\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:right\">[ Grace Before Meat, by Robert Burns ] </div>\n</div></div>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926184552\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.036 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.074 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 339/1000000\nPreprocessor generated